      "title": "Navy nabs 51 people attempting to illegally migrate from island",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A search operation in the eastern seas this morning (July 03) led to the seizure of a local multiday fishing trawler carrying 51 persons, who are suspected to be on an illegal migration attempt to a foreign country via sea, Sri Lanka Navy says."
